        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-red-600">1. Municipal Fines and Stop-Work Orders</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-700 mb-2">
              Toronto Building inspectors actively investigate unpermitted work based on neighbor complaints and routine surveillance. If caught:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Immediate stop-work order halting all construction</li>
              <li>Fines starting at $25,000 for first offense</li>
              <li>Additional fines of $10,000+ per day work continues</li>
