            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-red-600">2. Insurance Claim Denials</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-700 mb-2">
              Home insurance policies explicitly exclude coverage for unpermitted work. If structural problems arise:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Insurance will deny any claims related to the underpinning</li>
              <li>Water damage from foundation failures won't be covered</li>
